## shadcn/ui Components

- When adding new shadcn components, always use the following command format:
  ```bash
  npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>
  ```
- Never use `shadcn-ui@latest`
- Multiple components can be added in one command:
  ```bash
  npx shadcn@latest add badge scroll-area
  ```